What Are the Most Important Things Students Should Learn in School?

In your opinion, what are the most important things students should learn in school? What is the most important thing you have learned in school? How has this knowledge affected your life? How do you think it will help your success in the future?

---

In my opinion,

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I think this is the most important thing because the system affects all of our lives in a direct way, and we should know who does what and why

actions.text: Secondly, the belief that Trump will be reinstated as President is based in ignorance of the United States Constitution.

actions.text: This belief is the principle reason I think teaching people how our system works is the most important thing we can be learning in school.
